Linear Model with SSVS

m1_string <- textConnection("model{
  # Likelihood
  for(i in 1:n){
    Y[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    mu[i] <- alpha + inprod(X[i,],beta[])
  }
  
  # SSVS
  for(j in 1:p){
    beta[j] <- gamma[j]*delta[j]
    gamma[j] ~ dbern(0.5)
    delta[j] ~ dnorm(0,taud)
  }
  
  # Priors (weak)
  alpha ~ dnorm(0,0.01)
  taue  ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taud ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)

}")
m1 <- jags.model(m1_string, data = data_list, n.chains=2)

X_sub1 <- X[, c(1, 3:4, 7)]

names_sub1 <- c("alpha", colnames(X_sub1))
m2_string <- textConnection("model{
  # Likelihood
  for(i in 1:n){
    Y[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i],taue)
    mu[i] <- alpha + inprod(X[i,], beta[])
    Y2[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i],taue) # for PPC
    like[i] <- dnorm(Y[i], mu[i], taue) # for WAIC
  }
  
  # Priors
  for(j in 1:p){beta[j] ~ dnorm(0,0.001)}
  
  alpha ~ dnorm(0,0.01)
  taue  ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  
  # PPC
  Y2_sorted <- sort(Y2[])
  D[1] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.1 * n)] 
  D[2] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.5 * n)]  
  D[3] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.9 * n)]
}")
m2 <- jags.model(m2_string, data = data_list_sub1, n.chains=2)

Time-Varying Alpha LASSO

m3_string <- textConnection("model{
  # Likelihood
  for(i in 1:n){
    Y[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    mu[i] <- alpha[i] + inprod(X[i,], beta[])
    Y2[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    like[i] <- dnorm(Y[i], mu[i], taue)
  }

  # Random walk for alpha
  alpha[1] ~ dnorm(0, 0.01)
  for(i in 2:n){
    alpha[i] ~ dnorm(alpha[i-1], taua)
  }

  # LASSO
  for(j in 1:p){beta[j] ~ ddexp(0,taue*taub)}

  taua ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taub ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taue ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)

  # PPC
  Y2_sorted <- sort(Y2[])
  D[1] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.1 * n)]
  D[2] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.5 * n)]
  D[3] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.9 * n)]
}")
m3 <- jags.model(m3_string, data = data_list_sub1, n.chains=2)

Time-Varying Alpha and Beta

m4_string <- textConnection("model{
  # Likelihood
  for(i in 1:n){
    Y[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    mu[i] <- alpha[i] + inprod(X[i,], beta[i,])
    Y2[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    like[i] <- dnorm(Y[i], mu[i], taue)
  }

  # Random walk for alpha
  alpha[1] ~ dnorm(0, 0.01)
  for(i in 2:n){
    alpha[i] ~ dnorm(alpha[i-1], taua)
  }

  # Random walk for betas
  for(j in 1:p){
    beta[1, j] ~ dnorm(0, 0.01)
    for(i in 2:n){
      beta[i, j] ~ dnorm(beta[i-1, j], taub[j])
    }
    taub[j] ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  }

  taua ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taue ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)

  # PPC
  Y2_sorted <- sort(Y2[])
  D[1] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.1 * n)]
  D[2] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.5 * n)]
  D[3] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.9 * n)]
}")
m4 <- jags.model(m4_string, data = data_list_sub1, n.chains=2)

dataV2 <- data %>%
  select(Date, Mkt) %>%
  mutate( 
    vol = rollapply(Mkt, width = 3, FUN = sd, fill = NA,
                    align = "right"),

                             align = "right")

  select(Mkt, vol, mom)

## Warning: Unknown or uninitialised column: `Regime`.

## 
##  1  2  3  4

data <- na.omit(data)

X <- as.matrix(data[, c(3, 5:6, 9)])

regime <- as.vector(data$Regime)
n <- length(Y)

names <- colnames(X)

Model

m5_string <- textConnection("model{
  # Likelihood
  for(i in 1:n){
    Y[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    mu[i] <- alpha[i] + inprod(X[i,], beta[]) + theta[regime[i]]
    Y2[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    like[i] <- dnorm(Y[i], mu[i], taue)
  }

  # Random walk for alpha
  alpha[1] ~ dnorm(0, 0.01)
  for(i in 2:n){
    alpha[i] ~ dnorm(alpha[i-1], taua)
  }

  # LASSO
  for(j in 1:p){beta[j] ~ ddexp(0,taue*taub)}
  
  # Random effects
  for(k in 1:4) {theta[k] ~ dnorm(0,taut)}

  taua ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taub ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taue ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taut ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)

  # PPC
  Y2_sorted <- sort(Y2[])
  D[1] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.1 * n)]
  D[2] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.5 * n)]
  D[3] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.9 * n)]
}")
m5 <- jags.model(m5_string, data = data_list2, n.chains=2)

Time-Varying Alpha and Beta with Random Effects for Regime

Model

m6_string <- textConnection("model{
  # Likelihood
  for(i in 1:n){
    Y[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    mu[i] <- alpha[i] + inprod(X[i,], beta[i,]) + theta[regime[i]]
    Y2[i] ~ dnorm(mu[i], taue)
    like[i] <- dnorm(Y[i], mu[i], taue)
  }

  # Random walk for alpha
  alpha[1] ~ dnorm(0, 0.01)
  for(i in 2:n){
    alpha[i] ~ dnorm(alpha[i-1], taua)
  }

  # Random walk for betas
  for(j in 1:p){
    beta[1, j] ~ dnorm(0, 0.01)
    for(i in 2:n){
      beta[i, j] ~ dnorm(beta[i-1, j], taub[j])
    }
    taub[j] ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  }
  
  # Random effects
  for(k in 1:4) {theta[k] ~ dnorm(0,taut)}

  taua ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taue ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)
  taut ~ dgamma(0.1, 0.1)

  # PPC
  Y2_sorted <- sort(Y2[])
  D[1] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.1 * n)]
  D[2] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.5 * n)]
  D[3] <- Y2_sorted[round(0.9 * n)]
}")
m6 <- jags.model(m6_string, data = data_list2, n.chains=2)
